common_issues.title: Pieces Core Services Unauthenticated User Exception
common_issues.description: Users are unable to open Pieces Core Services due to an UnauthenticatedUserException.  This might be related to Pieces OS version 12.2.1 on MacOS 15.6.1. Verify user authentication status and ensure proper login credentials are used. Check for any conflicting software or recent system updates that may interfere with Pieces Core Services.

recommendations: Investigate the "Pieces Core Services Unauthenticated User Exception" error. It's affecting MacOS 15.6.1 users with Pieces OS version 12.2.1 and preventing them from opening Pieces Core Services.
Prioritize resolving issue #855, "Unable to open Pieces Core Services", as it has the highest activity level and is likely impacting multiple users.
Check for potential conflicts with other software or recent system updates on MacOS 15.6.1 that might interfere with Pieces Core Services.
Verify user authentication status and ensure proper login credentials are being used by affected users.
Review the error logs related to the UnauthenticatedUserException to identify the root cause and potential solutions.
